# Digital Twin Assistant — Implementation Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A fully self-contained AI conversational interface at **`public/ai-assistant/`**, completely isolated from the main WebXR viewport. Once stable, the underlying logic can be ported directly into the 3D immersive view.

---

## File Structure

```
lathe-trainer/
├── public/
│   └── ai-assistant/
│       ├── index.html   ← HTML shell + layout
│       ├── style.css    ← Full design system (Vanilla CSS, design tokens)
│       └── main.js      ← All application logic (no npm deps)
