## Opening the Playground

The dev server is running. Navigate to:

```
https://localhost:8081/ai-assistant/
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Use **HTTPS** (not HTTP) — the dev server uses mkcert TLS. `SpeechRecognition` and `SpeechSynthesis` APIs require a secure context.

